# Conductor: keep workspace-local state ignored but track the shared repo config.
# (.conductor/ is excluded by a global gitignore; re-include the shared file so
# teammates pick it up. Conductor's per-workspace files under .conductor/ stay ignored.)
!.conductor/
.conductor/*
!.conductor/settings.toml

